title: Wyrd Sisters (Discworld #6)
description: Storyline: Wyrd Sisters (Discworld #6) \n Witches are not by nature gregarious, and they certainly don't have leaders. Granny Weatherwax was the most highly-regarded of the leaders they didn't have. But even she found that meddling in royal politics was a lot more difficult than certain playwrights would have you believe...\n
author: Terry Pratchett
